exercise.statement:
The total amount of CO_{2} that the U.S.A. emits can be found by multiplying the amount that each person 
emits with the total U.S.\ population. Find and simplify a formula for T(t), the total amount of CO_{2} 
released by the U.S.A., in millions of metric tons, t years since 2000.

